title: Trends with Friends 6/17: Felony Murder, McMuffin, Pete Hunziker, Earthquake
itunes:title: Trends with Friends 6/17: Felony Murder, McMuffin, Pete Hunziker, Earthquake
description:
On this edition of Trends with Friends Miles and Laci discuss the officer who murdered Rayshard Brooks being charged with Felony Murder, a Police officer complained on the internet about their McMuffin coming too slowly, another member of the Below Deck show has been fired for being racist, and there was a 3.6 magnitude Earthquake in the Bay.
